snippet.title: (Game Trailer) The 2030 Proto-Interfacer's Guide to House-Oriented Emotional Exploration
snippet.description:
This is a "Cinematic" trailer which means it's full of lies and deception. You can play the game @ https://sq-com.itch.io/house-exploration-2030
Originally posted as Unlisted in November of 2022. Although filming and prep were significantly earlier than even that, I'm fairly sure.
Song is "At the Rasco" by Charlie Megira. If you see external ads on the video that's the label's fault!
